            k_eff = 3.183 rad/m  (= k_c from M19 cliff)

--- 5b. Layer 2 -- D20 Operations (M8L) ---
  Transit capacity: 47 tx/hr, 604.3 ly/hr
  Destinations: 12  |  Routes: 30 (DOCK_A bidirectional)
  First transit: H01->Proxima Centauri 7.71 ns
